column5: Hi all,  Had another really crappie morning on Saturday.
Mmmmmgood. What is all that white stuff you are standing on Simon? 16C this afternoon on Ontario's southern coast.
Dear god. Your fishing days are what dreams are made of. Another beautiful day out.
I had a crappie morning too.....from my boat lol
Right on! I got into a few openwater crappie and bullhead last night.
Cheers to you for still ice fishing - I wish we had a few more days of ice!
